FBIS3-56423 "drsov011_b_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-011 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues To Leave Government LD1801123394 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1200 GMT 18 Jan 94 LD1801123394 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] INTERFAX has reported that Boris Fedorov has declined the proposal by Viktor Chernomyrdin that he join the reorganized government of Russia as Minister of Finance. However, he has not offered to resign from any of the posts he occupies. Boris Fedorov is currently a Vice-Premier and Minister of Finance of Russia.
